title: Pencils of Promise
description: Pencils of Promise believes every child should have access to quality education. We create schools, programs and global communities around the common goal of education for all.

title: UNICEF - SURGE
description: SURGE is an immersive series of events that invites youth to learn new skills, while at the same time exploring where blockchain could play a role in addressing global challenges.

title: UNICEF - Giga
description: Giga is a global initiative to connect every school to the internet and every young person to information, opportunity, and choice.

title: Handshake Development Fund (Panvala League)
description: Handshake is a completely community-run decentralized blockchain built to dismantle ICANN's monopoly on top-level domains (.com, .net, .org, etc. are all top-level domains controlled by ICANN, who charges an $185,000 evaluation fee.
